WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: ja

00:00:26.266 --> 00:00:30.986
唇、あの人には 届かないし
With your lip movements you can’t reach anyone,

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:36.480
探しても無駄なんじゃないかな？
so isn’t it pointless even if you tried to?

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:41.440
君が息を吹き返したら
While you seem to breathe freely

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:47.106
逆に息を潜めた僕
I toned down my breathing.

00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:48.973
知ってる
I knew that

00:00:48.970 --> 00:00:52.360
君は死んでない
you’re not dead.

00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:57.493
僕には 関係ないよ
It doesn’t matter to me.

00:00:57.490 --> 00:00:59.293
なるべく
I don’t really

00:00:59.290 --> 00:01:02.653
会いたくないな
want to see you.

00:01:02.650 --> 00:01:06.066
たじろぐ姿は
Your wincing

00:01:06.060 --> 00:01:12.146
好きの証
proofs you like me.

00:01:12.573 --> 00:01:15.066
臆病なだけなのに
I’m not more than a coward

00:01:15.060 --> 00:01:18.120
ロマンチスト気取り
and yet a romanticist; not a

00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:22.786
じゃないと身が持たないし
feigned one and I don’t belong to myself.

00:01:22.780 --> 00:01:25.413
でもまたすぐに
But again I’ll

00:01:25.410 --> 00:01:28.013
後悔してる
regret it right after.

00:01:28.010 --> 00:01:33.133
学習能力はゼロ
My ability to learn equals zero.

00:01:33.360 --> 00:01:35.213
普段は
Usually I’m

00:01:35.210 --> 00:01:38.640
ずる賢いよ
really devious.

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:43.826
君には通用しない
That doesn’t apply to you.

00:01:43.820 --> 00:01:48.986
口から口に注ぎたい
I want to show you mouth-to-mouth,

00:01:48.980 --> 00:01:50.693
ダメだろ
but I shouldn’t

00:01:50.690 --> 00:01:58.853
無抵抗だし　今は
although you’re defenseless now…

00:02:19.426 --> 00:02:21.786
こんな状況でも
You think this way about me

00:02:21.780 --> 00:02:24.546
変な気持ちになる
but it starts to feel strange.

00:02:24.540 --> 00:02:26.960
間違いなんて
Without a doubt

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:29.706
気にしない
I don’t care.

00:02:29.700 --> 00:02:32.253
がむしゃらでした
It was reckless.

00:02:32.250 --> 00:02:34.693
さよならはヤダ
I don’t want to bid farewell.

00:02:34.690 --> 00:02:39.986
定めらぬうちに触れた
I can’t decide if you touched me within.

